100 towns of populations under 1,500 in America.

23
00:02:17,845 --> 00:02:18,861
(group chuckling and clapping)

24
00:02:18,861 --> 00:02:21,260
That's wonderful.

25
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:22,390
Obviously, we're,

26
